.ui.container#activity.hidden
  .ui.container#know-you-read
    .limit
      h1.ui.header.large#learn-title
        .content 
          i.dice.icon
          | Activity: Select the appropriate option.

        .ui.grid(style=" margin-top: 10px;")
          .two.column.row
            .column
              p.ui.container
                button.ui.button.fluid#wrong-bttn-1(onclick="showAnswer1()", style="font-size: 20px;") Set your account to public mode to attract as many followers as possible.

            .column
              p.ui.container
                button.ui.button.fluid#correct-bttn-1(onclick="showAnswer1()", style="font-size: 20px;") Set your account to private mode to prevent strangers from reaching you.

          .two.column.row
            .column
              p.ui.container
                button.ui.button.fluid#wrong-bttn-2(onclick="showAnswer2()", style="font-size: 20px;") To identify whether the caller is actually your grandchild, pay attention to the caller’s voice. If the voice sounds identical or very similar, it’s safe to believe the caller is indeed your grandchild.
              
            .column
              p.ui.container
                button.ui.button.fluid#correct-bttn-2(onclick="showAnswer2()", style="font-size: 20px;") To identify whether the caller is actually your grandchild, establish and use a secret code, question, or nickname known only to you and your grandchild.


          .two.column.row
            .column
              p.ui.container
                button.ui.button.fluid#correct-bttn-3(onclick="showAnswer3()", style="font-size: 20px;") You identified the call as a scam, but you chose not to report it or inform others about it since you weren’t deceived by the scam.

              
            .column
              p.ui.container
                button.ui.button.fluid#wrong-bttn-3(onclick="showAnswer3()", style="font-size: 20px;") Although you recognized the scam call and weren’t deceived, you chose to report it and inform your family about it since you don’t want them to be scammed.

script.
  function showAnswer1() {
    $('#correct-bttn-1').css({
      'background-color': '#E3F2DC',
      'border': '2px solid #6F8C5A'
    });
    $('#wrong-bttn-1').css({
      'background-color': '#F2CECE',
      'border': '2px solid #F24141'
    });
  }

  function showAnswer2() {
    $('#correct-bttn-2').css({
      'background-color': '#E3F2DC',
      'border': '2px solid #6F8C5A'
    });
    $('#wrong-bttn-2').css({
      'background-color': '#F2CECE',
      'border': '2px solid #F24141'
    });
  }

  function showAnswer3() {
    $('#correct-bttn-3').css({
      'background-color': '#E3F2DC',
      'border': '2px solid #6F8C5A'
    });
    $('#wrong-bttn-3').css({
      'background-color': '#F2CECE',
      'border': '2px solid #F24141'
    });
  }

